Based on the definition https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man5/os-release.5.html, os-release follow format , which includes well defined keywords, which can be used for user to extract the required driver info. Not seeing any predefined keywords related redundant driver info. I think best approach would be be create new secondary-os-release file , and follow the same format mentioned in os-release document ion. which will help user to extract the data automatically. This will help to move this plugin to common place instead of IBM specific path. 
@adriana @gmills @lieu please add your view on this.

@swarnedu if it is IBM custom plugin, am fine with format which meets ibm requirement.
